SMART CURRICULUM ACTIVITY AND ATTENDANCE APP
The Smart Curriculum Activity and Attendance App is a digital solution designed to simplify and automate the management of student attendance and academic activities. 
This application helps teachers efficiently record attendance, track curriculum progress, and monitor student participation in various academic and extracurricular activities.

Simple core features
Student login
Teacher login
Mark attendance
View attendance report
Add curriculum activities

Common tools:
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (or Android Studio for mobile)
Backend: Java / PHP / Node.js
Database: MySQL / Firebase

Basic Modules of the App
📌 Admin Module
Add teachers
Add students
Manage subjects
View attendance reports
📌 Teacher Module
Mark student attendance
Add curriculum activities
View student attendance
📌 Student Module
View attendance
View activity updates
Notifications
